parameters:
Taiyo-senpai, who was grinning while staring at the disposable
chopsticks with a black tip that he had pulled out
himself, looked at me and said.
Go for a walk outside in areas 3 and 5.
Make sure to go for at least 30 minutes.

Judging from the expression they were giving me while staring,
it was clear that they had done something with their
hands and manipulated the lottery.

The two of them seem the most awkward in our circle. They
should try to get along a little better.

That's how we were pushed by Senpai Taiyo and driven out to
the sandy beach.
